      • copulate

        <A extends Mammal> void copulate(A animal,
                                 int turnNb)
        Allows an animal to perform a copulation with the one given in arg
        Type Parameters:
        A - Generic type of Mammal to force having a Mammal as first arg
        Parameters:
        animal - The animal that will perform the copulation with our current Animal instance
        turnNb - The current turn number, used in case the copulation succeed, to calculate how long to pregnancy will last
